Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.96,0:49:15.98,倒數,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(0,0,255,0,0,0000,1000)}{\t(0,0,1,\fscx200\fscy200)}4
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.98,0:49:16.94,倒數,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(0,0,255,0,0,0000,1000)}{\t(0,0,1,\fscx200\fscy200)}3
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.94,0:49:17.90,倒數,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(0,0,255,0,0,0000,1000)}{\t(0,0,1,\fscx200\fscy200)}2
